---
import { SITE } from '../config/site';
---

<section id="positioning" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-16">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-x-12 items-center">
    <!-- Left content -->
    <div class="md:col-span-7">
      <div class="inline-block px-3.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-xs tracking-[1.5px] font-medium text-white/60 mb-4">THE OPPORTUNITY</div>

      <h2 class="section-header tracking-[-0.04em] leading-none mb-7">
        The next generation<br />
        needs new standards.
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-white/80 max-w-[42ch]">
        <p>
          As AI capabilities accelerate, the organizations building the future need secure frameworks that are as modern, adaptable, and forward-thinking as the systems they protect.
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="font-semibold text-white">secureaiframeworks.xyz</span> is the clean, contemporary domain for next-generation secure AI frameworks — tools, platforms, and approaches designed for the teams shaping what comes next.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70">
          It signals innovation, tech fluency, and a commitment to building security that keeps pace with rapid AI advancement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right visual card -->
    <div class="md:col-span-5 mt-10 md:mt-0">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl p-9 md:p-10">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#22f5ff20] to-[#a855f720] border border-white/20 mb-6">
            <span class="font-display text-sm font-bold tracking-[-0.5px] bg-gradient-to-br from-[#22f5ff] to-[#a855f7] bg-clip-text text-transparent">XYZ</span>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-1">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter">Secure AI Frameworks</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/60 tracking-[2px] mt-1">MODERN • INNOVATIVE • NEXT-GEN</div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-white/10 text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            The domain for teams<br />
            building what comes next.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
